sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Admin/Superadmin
    participant App as Flutter app
    participant ApiService
    participant API as FastAPI /tasks
    participant Media as Media helpers
    participant Files as uploads/
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant TG as Telegram Bot API
    participant FCM as Firebase Cloud Messaging

    Admin->>App: Створює задачу з виконавцями і файлами
    App->>ApiService: createTask(text, executorIds, files)
    ApiService->>API: POST /tasks multipart/form-data
    API->>DB: insert Task
    API->>DB: insert TaskAssignment rows
    loop кожен файл
        API->>Files: write upload
        API->>Media: normalize video / extract duration
        API->>DB: insert TaskMedia
    end
    API->>DB: commit transaction
    API->>DB: select assigned users
    loop кожен отримувач
        alt має telegram_id
            API->>TG: send task message/media
        end
        alt має fcm_token
            API->>FCM: send new_task push
        end
    end
    API-->>ApiService: TaskResponse
    ApiService-->>App: success
